# SEC (SECURITY.md B-1): the agent config carries the ase-mcp bearer token, which
# is a host-RCE credential (run_lua executes arbitrary Lua with os.execute in the
# Aseprite plugin environment). NEVER commit it. .mcp.json.example is the template.
.mcp.json

# Build artifacts. The bundled server binary and the packaged extension are NOT
# tracked (SECURITY.md A-8: installing them = trusting them). Build from source
# with build_exe.bat / build_package.py; verify against the SHA256 in SECURITY.md.
*.exe
*.aseprite-extension
dist/
build/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/

# local runtime
*.log

# local working files (demo assets, agent graph caches, scratch prompts)
assets/
graphify-out/
prompt-test.txt
